    "description": "<p>Few prosper or survive in the service and worship of the Dark Gods thanks to their cruelty, capriciousness and thirst for human life. Those that do are fanatics, dark souls who have given themselves over utterly to the worship of Chaos, steeped in sin and depravity and far from sane. Although often undisciplined and unskilled in the arts of warfare, they are nevertheless extraordinarily dangerous, particularly in large numbers, because they are without fear and willing to die for their foul gods. They stop at nothing, no matter how horrific the deed, in the name of Chaos.</p><p><strong>Skills:</strong> Awareness (Per), Climb (S), Speak Language (Low Gothic, Unholy Tongue) (Int), Swim (S), Survival (Int).</p><p><strong>Talents:</strong> Berserk Charge, Furious Assault, Melee Weapon Training (Primitive), Pistol Training (SP).</p><p><strong>Traits:</strong> Resistance (Fear).</p><p><strong>Source:</strong> Deathwatch Core Rulebook, p. 364</p>",
